                <li>All the required scripts are included in the correct order.</li>
                <li>The hash of each file is appended to each URL as a "cache-breaker".</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="minor">The SHA-1 hash is used. The output here has been shortened to fit on screen.</p>
        </div>

